      "content": "hey can u help me put together a quick itinerary for a business trip to tokyo next week? i'll be staying near shibuya but most of my meetings are in the marunouchi area. i need to know how long it actually takes to get between them during the day and also could u suggest a few quiet cafes in those areas where i can actually get some work done? thanks",
